channel.title: TitanPK Glacors
channel.description:
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cXmOUvZsxYs&feature=plcp]TitanPK 718 Glacors - YouTube[/url]
Been working on these for 2 days. I don't think it is completely worth a showoff because it took no real programming ability to complete (just simple logic and some IDs). I haven't seen someone complete these on any other server so I thought I might show mine off.
If you watch the video all the way through, you will see some people who have never killed glacors on real RS before trying to kill them on my server and they start raging saying they are too strong :P
